---
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Wikilear, tutorial e codelab
hide_title: false
description: "Notizie, tutorial e codelab alla portata di tutti."
subtitle:
image:
pagination:
  data: collections.feed
  size: 3
permalink: "{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}/page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}{% endif %}/"
paginationPrevText: "Articoli più recenti"
paginationNextText: "Articoli più vecchi"
paginationAnchor: "#all-articles"
feed: ""
schema:
  type: WebSite
---

{% block content %}
<div>
  <img
    src="/images/home.jpg"
    alt="Concetto di apprendimento online"
    class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg"
    data-lcp="high"
  />
</div>
<article class="mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4">
  <div id="all-articles" class="heading my-2">
    {% set postListItems = pagination.items %} {% include
    "partials/post-list.njk" %} {% include "partials/pagination.njk" %}
  </div>
</article>
<nav
  id="topics"
  class="heading my-8 mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4 text-center border rounded-lg shadow-lg font-bold"
>

  <h2 class="mt-4 font-bold">Argomenti principali</h2>
  {% include 'components/card.njk' %}

</nav>

{% set cards = [
  { url: "/blog/", image: "/images/blog-post.svg", title: "Blog"},
  { url: "/tips-and-tricks/", image: "/images/undraw_team_up_ip2x.png", title: "Tips and tricks"},
  { url: "/termini-uso-privacy/", image: "/images/undraw_privacy_protection_nlwy.png", title: "Termini d'uso e privacy"},
  { url: "/tutorial/", image: "/images/tutorial.svg", title: "Tutorial"}
] %}

<nav id="sections" aria-label="Sezioni prinicipali del sito">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4 my-4 gap-y-8">
    {% for card in cards %}
    <a class="w-full sm:w-5/11" href="{{ card.url }}">
      <div
        class="h-full mb-6 flex flex-col border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-300 border rounded-lg shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-t-lg bg-gray-800 text-white">
          <p class="text-center m-2">{{ card.title }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="h-full relative pb-2/3">
          <img
            class="p-6 sm:p-4 absolute h-full object-cover"
            src="{{ card.image }}"
            alt
            sizes="(max-width:640px) 300px, 600px"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</nav>

<article
  class="my-8 mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4 text-center border rounded-lg shadow-lg font-semibold"
>
  <details class="cursor-pointer" open>
    <summary id="tags" class="heading m-4 font-bold">Tutte le etichette</summary>
    {% include 'components/tagsList/tags-list.njk' %}
  </details>
</article>

<p>
  Wikilear è un progetto open source creato con
  <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" aria-label="Eleventy (link al sito)">Eleventy</a> e
  <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/" aria-label="Tailwind CSS (link al sito)">Tailwind CSS,</a>
  è ospitato su <a href="https://www.netlify.com/">Netlify,</a> trovi il codice sorgente su <a href="https://github.com/andrealeardini/wikilear" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub.</a> Wikilear è stato testato
  sui più moderni browser: Chrome, Edge e Firefox. Su Safari potresti
  riscontrare qualche problema a livello grafico.
</p>
{% endblock %}